  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Winterization Response in Place of Origin in Muqur and Bala Murghab Districts of Badghis Province</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Project Activities: 
The project will build the resilience of 1800 drought-affected IDPs and returnee HHs to cope with the upcoming harsh winter and reduce suffering. 
&#x2022;	Distribution of cash for heating/fuel to 1200 HHs
&#x2022;	Distribution of cash for emergency NFIs to 882 HHs
&#x2022;	Distribution of cash for transportation for voluntarily return to the place origin to 600 HHs
&#x2022;	Distribution of cash for shelter/house upgrade/repair to 600 newly returned HHs in Muqur district</narrative>
  </description>
